---
title: Spinach Salad with Salmon & Couscous plus Marinated Tomatoes, Roasted Carrots & Pistachios
description: When the mood strikes, a big dinner salad is exactly the right meal at the right time. And this one is everything you love about spanakopita—and then some—in salad form! You’ll toss earthy cumin-roasted carrots and sweet red onion with bouncy, garlicky pearl couscous, leafy spinach, and juicy marinated grape tomatoes. It’s all dressed in a tangy vinaigrette and topped with briny crumbled feta and crunchy, nutty pistachios. In the mood yet?
